First Department,

October, 1938.

(October 7, 1938.) In the Matter of Supplementary Proceedings: Grace Herlihy, Judgment Creditor, Respondent, v. J. L. Watkins, Judgment Debtor. In the Matter of Supplementary Proceedings: 50 East 72nd Street Corporation, Judgment Creditor, Appellant, v. J. Lawrence Watkins, Jr., Judgment Debtor.

Order, so far as appealed from, unanimously affirmed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., O’Malley, Glennon, Untermyer and Cohn, JJ.
